        <mxCell id="p3" value="収束：BL点灯→現像メモ『凶行の半刻のち』＋覚書『半刻=30分』＋止時計03:45 → dial『04:15』（囮：予備時計04:45）" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#999999;align=left;spacingLeft=8;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="60" y="378" width="460" height="76" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
